    //    3.2. Select the parent theme name. Your new theme will inherit the properties of parent theme.
    //    3.3. After creating a new theme styles folder under the values folder will be updated with
    //         two styles.xml(styles.xml-> AppCompat Themes, styles.xml (v21) -> Material Design Themes).




